a_n = \sqrt{2+ \frac{3}{n}}
\left|\sqrt{2+ \frac{3}{n}} - \sqrt{2}\right| \le \varepsilon
\sqrt{2+ \frac{3}{n}} - \sqrt{2}= \frac{3/n}{\sqrt{2 + \frac{3}{n}} + \sqrt{2}}
\frac{3/n}{2 \sqrt{2}} \le \varepsilon
\sqrt{2 + \frac{3}{n}}
\sqrt{2}
\sqrt{2 +\frac{3}{n}} + \sqrt{2}
2\sqrt{2}
\frac{1}{\sqrt{2+\frac{3}{n}}+\sqrt{2}}
\frac{1}{2\sqrt{2}}
